abstract: Nomadic group in Britain known as travelers leave site where they have lived illegally for a decade, ending days of fierce resistance and lengthy legal battle against authorities who forced their eviction.
snippet: A nomadic group known as travelers left the Dale Farm site in Britain on Thursday, where they had lived illegally for a decade.
lead_paragraph: A nomadic group known as travelers left the Dale Farm site in Britain on Thursday, where they had lived illegally for a decade.
